divs: Sighting DetailsI found this,this year and this is the only place I could find to report anything on it.Its not a ufo sighting.It could be just a rock but it sure does look like a alien skull to everyone I've shown it to.I am submitting photos and hope someone contacts me on this because it could be the oldest fossilized alien skull ever found.I put some deer skulls by it to show size.It just looks to real not to be.
